	Sick lie detector    
	 London, May 15 (PTI): Those in the habit of calling in sick will need to improve their proficiency in the art of lying for bosses determined to check absenteeism in office are resorting to technology to crack down on employees pulling a sickie.       
	The technology ensures that someone phoning in for a sick leave will speak to a computer set up to check whether their voice is steady and reliable. The voice risk analysis picks up changes in a callers voice that suggest they are under pressure  as is likely if they are lying.     
