	 London (Reuters): Actor Hugh Grant, his ex-girlfriend Liz Hurley and her businessman husband Arun Nayar won 58,000 in damages on Thursday after paparazzi pictures taken while they were on a holiday in the Maldives were published in tabloid newspapers.                                                                                                                                                                           
